{"article_id":"ruaTYWoIHaToDbw3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Dr. Anthony Fauci , the nation 's top infectious disease expert , told lawmakers Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"that the US will be increasing coronavirus testing ,","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"saying ,","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"`` we 're going to be doing more testing , not less , ''","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"in response to President Donald Trump 's recent claim","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"that he asked his administration to slow down testing during the pandemic .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"The testimony from Fauci , director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases , came during a House Energy and Commerce Committee hearing on the Trump administration 's response to the coronavirus pandemic","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"`` To my knowledge , none of us have ever been told to slow down on testing .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"That just is a fact .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"In fact , we will be doing more testing , ''","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Fauci said on a witness panel of top officials from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention , the Food and Drug Administration and the Department of Health and Human Services .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"The spotlight is on testing","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"after the President said in a shocking admission during his Tulsa , Oklahoma , rally on Saturday night","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that he had told officials in his administration to slow down coronavirus testing","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"because of the rising number of cases in the country .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"`` When you do testing to that extent ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"you 're going to find more people ;","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"you 're going to find more cases .","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"So I said to my people ,","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"slow the testing down please , ''","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"After the President made the comment ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"multiple White House officials said","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"that the President was joking .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"But Trump told a reporter on Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"`` I do n't kid ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"let me just tell you ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"let me make it clear , ''","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"when asked again","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"if he was joking in his remarks over the weekend .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"That was n't the only time","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that Fauci broke with the President during the hearing .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Asked if he has concerns about the President 's decision","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to terminate the US relationship with the World Health Organization ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Fauci responded ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"`` Yes , I do , ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"adding ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` Despite any policy issues","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that come from higher up in the White House ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"we at the operational level continue to interact with the WHO in a very meaningful way , literally on a day by day basis . ''","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Fauci gave a broad assessment","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"of where the country stands amid the pandemic ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"warning","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that in some areas of the United States , `` we 're now seeing a disturbing surge of infections . ''","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"the next couple of weeks `` are going to be critical in our ability","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"to address those surges","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that we 're seeing in Florida , in Texas , in Arizona , and in other states .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"They 're not the only ones","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"that are having a difficulty . ''","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Fauci , the director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases , is testifying along with CDC Director Dr. Robert Redfield , HHS Assistant Secretary for Health Brett Giroir and FDA Commissioner Dr. Stephen Hahn .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"The hearing comes","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"as the country continues to grapple with the devastating public health consequences of the pandemic ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"which has already claimed the lives of over 120,000 in the US .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Asked to assess the likelihood","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"of developing a vaccine ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"Fauci said","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"`` I feel cautiously optimistic","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that we will be successful","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"in getting a vaccine , ''","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"adding ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"`` I still think","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"there is a reasonably good chance","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that by the very beginning of 2021 that ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"if we 're going to have a vaccine ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that we will have it by then . ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Fauci has no regrets","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"about not telling Americans to wear masks sooner","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Fauci said during the hearing","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that he does not regret the timing","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"of when he told Americans to wear masks ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"explaining how the situation was different","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"when concerns over shortages of personal protective equipment , or PPE , were more acute .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"`` I do n't regret that","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"-- because","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"let me explain to you what happened .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"At that time , there was a paucity of equipment","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"that our health care providers needed --","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"who put themselves daily in harm 's way","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"of taking care of people","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"who are ill.","depth":17},{"id":82,"text":"We did not want to divert masks and PPE away from them ,","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"to be used by the people , ''","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"`` Now that we have enough ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"we recommend ... ``","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Fauci began answering","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"before he was cut off for the next question .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Fauci told lawmakers during the hearing","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"that American 's should avoid going into crowds ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"but","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"if they must ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"they should wear a mask .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"For those","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"who do go against public health guidance","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"of avoiding crowds ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Fauci urged ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"`` Please wear a mask .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"as you wear a mask ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"and you 're in a situation","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"where you 're getting animated in a demonstration or in a rally or wherever you are ,","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"avoid","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"-- as best as possible --","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"the urge","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"to pull your mask down","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and shout . ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Fauci said ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"`` Plan A :","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Do n't go in a crowd .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"Plan B :","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"If you do ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"make sure","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"you wear a mask . ''","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"CDC director says","depth":3},{"id":116,"text":"virus has 'brought this nation to its knees '","depth":3},{"id":117,"text":"Covid-19 has `` brought this nation to its knees , ''","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"Redfield said Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"`` We 've all done the best","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"that we can do","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"to tackle this virus , ''","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"he said during the hearing .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"But Redfield said","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"that the virus has highlighted decades of underinvesting in the `` core capabilities of public health data .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"'' Now is the time","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"to fix the broken system ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"`` This needs to be a partnership .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"It 's not all the burden of the federal government to invest in public health at the local level , ''","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Redfield said .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"In reality , `` if your funding of CDC was to go away tomorrow ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"public health infrastructure across this nation would just crash . ''","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Redfield also said on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"that getting a flu shot this year will save lives .","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"`` CDC has begun to prepare for months ahead ,","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"when the next season 's influenza illness will occur simultaneously , potentially , with Covid-19 ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"increasing the challenges on hospitals , health care professionals and the public , ''","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"Redfield said .","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"`` This fall ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"before the seasonal circulation of influenza increase ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"I encourage the American people to be prepared","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"and to embrace flu vaccination with confidence for yourself , your families in the communities , ''","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"`` This single act will save lives . ''","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"Institutional racism in the United States contributes to the disproportional impact","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"that the coronavirus pandemic has had on the Black community ,","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"Fauci , said on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"that the Black community has been facing a `` double whammy . ''","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"Fauci noted","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"that some Black adults may not be able to social distance","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"if they are essential workers ,","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"and there is a disproportionate prevalence of underlying conditions within the Black community , such as hypertension , diabetes , obesity , chronic lung disease and kidney disease .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"`` So unfortunately we have a situation","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"where it 's sort of a double whammy , ''","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"Fauci said .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"`` Obviously , the African American community has suffered from racism for a very , very long period of time , ''","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"Fauci said .","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"`` I ca n't imagine","depth":6},{"id":160,"text":"that that is not contributing to the conditions","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"that they find themselves in , economically or otherwise . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":323,"left":276,"right":322,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":0,"right":275,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":275,"left":215,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":215,"left":201,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201